---
title: Chicken Breast Korma Style Curry with Baby Spinach and Garlic Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chicken Breast Korma Style Curry in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W11_UK_G1571716538-8_Main_low-506e3c7d.jpg
